"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-11-30-Olympic-badminton-champion-Zheng-to-retire-from-international-events-1yWFMuN4L7y-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sporte Scene  Copied  File photo of Zheng Siwei.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zheng Siwei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  China's Olympic mixed doubles badminton gold medalist Zheng Siwei announced that he will retire from international competition on Friday.\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 260, \"end\": 265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9978926221745466, \"rank\": 0.0020132132141464473, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 314, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zheng Siwei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next month's BWF World Tour Finals in Hangzhou will be his \\\"last dance\\\".\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BWF_World_Tour_Finals\", \"score\": 0.9980331415938486, \"rank\": 0.0019689097188925917, \"text\": \"BWF World Tour Finals\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BWF_World_Tour_Finals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BWF_World_Tour_Finals\"}, {\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 0.9999999985211616, \"rank\": 1.1490228428292407e-09, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Many people expected me to play at least until the Los Angeles Olympics, or even longer.\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6129214655549672, \"rank\": 0.6315303936933866, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If there were any questions about our competitiveness, we just won the Olympic gold and rank among the top in the world rankings.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for why I suddenly want to stop playing, my answer is, this is my life plan,\\\" the 27-year-old wrote on Chinese social media platform Weibo.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 798, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9774586416377176, \"rank\": 0.022614726410787715, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sina_Weibo\", \"score\": 0.9992154005728915, \"rank\": 0.0007356263816941076, \"text\": \"Weibo\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sina_Weibo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sina_Weibo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zheng Siwei (L) and Huang Yaqiong celebrate winning mixed doubles gold at the Paris Olympics in Paris, France, August 2, 2024.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 836, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zheng Siwei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\"}, {\"begin\": 856, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huang Yaqiong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\"}, {\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999191695711, \"rank\": 8.083046977495143e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9870845249098404, \"rank\": 0.007643553857535937, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  Zheng mentioned returning to his family as one of the most important reasons for his decision: \\\"My life goals are now focussed on my family and career.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 969, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999999783881324, \"rank\": 2.1185032392623337e-08, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone knows that I married relatively early, and now I have just had a second baby, so I want to return to the family.\\\"\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After claiming silver at the Tokyo Olympics three years ago, Zheng and his partner Huang Yaqiong won mixed doubles gold at the Paris Olympics, finishing the tournament with a perfect 6-0 record, and not losing a single set.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999999783881324, \"rank\": 2.1185032392623337e-08, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}, {\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huang Yaqiong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Along the way, we constantly made breakthroughs and broke records.\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We faced challenges and doubts, but we never stopped and we finally won a Grand Slam,\\\" wrote Zheng.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999999783881324, \"rank\": 2.1185032392623337e-08, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}